									{
										"data": [
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "AnimationTags"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[KAYLEIGH] Wyll, panicking and in pain, morphs into a lemure., , ............................................., [AMN][GUS-218128] Wyll falls down on his knees...body spasming from the change. His head is bowed down as he endures the physical transformation., , In horror he notices the change on both his hands. He sits back and looks at them. He then sees the rest of his body., , He gets up to his feet and really looks at himself. He then hesitatingly reaches both hands up to touch his face. He shudders in shock and disgust at the changes he felt there., , (Note: Tom had shot a really fantastic video of himself acting out the transformation beats. We could also use that video as reference)"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "Attitude"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Default"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Fire begins to engulf Wyll. He is in agony."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
